settings.title: Wholesale & Retail Healthcare with Platinum Health
settings.description: At Platinum Health Supply Group, we're more than just a healthcare supplier; we're your dedicated partner in improving quality of life.

settings.text: Apply for a Wholesale account by filling out your details below.
settings.industry_options: NDIS| Home Caring| Healthcare| Aged Care| Government| Education| Distributor| Manufacturers| Retail | Construction| Logistics |

settings.title: Why Choose Platinum Health for Your Wholesale Healthcare Needs?
Tiered Pricing
settings.description: We believe in rewarding loyalty. As a Platinum partner, you'll enjoy exclusive tiered pricing based on your monthly spend. The more you invest in us, the more you save.

settings.title: Same-Day Dispatch
settings.description: Time is of the essence, especially in healthcare. All orders placed before 1 pm are dispatched on the same day, ensuring you receive critical supplies promptly.

settings.title: Free Shipping
settings.description: We're dedicated to your convenience. Orders over $399 (excluding Furniture & Fittings, + Rehabilitation & Mobility Range) qualify for free shipping, so you can focus on what matters most - care.

settings.title: Premium Quality, Proven Results
settings.description: With over 8000+ products available and backed by 3000+ five-star reviews, our commitment to premium-quality healthcare is validated by our satisfied customers.

settings.title: Dedicated Account Manager
settings.description: Your journey with us is personalised. Access a dedicated account manager who will handle your inquiries, ensuring you have a seamless experience.

settings.title: Loyalty Program
settings.description: Because your loyalty matters, we've designed a loyalty program that rewards you for the trust you place in our products. Your purchases not only improve lives but also earn you valuable rewards.
